Title: Meeuwen sterven in de haven
Director: Rik Kuypers, Ivo Michiels, Roland Verhavert
Writer: Rik Kuypers (scenario), Ivo Michiels (scenario), Roland Verhavert (scenario)
Actors: Tine Balder, Tone Brulin, Alice De Graef, Jenny Deheyder
Plot: A pessimistic urban drama, with a musical score by Jack Sels and Max Damasse, charts in strongly expressionistically lit black-and-white images the wanderings of a tormented man through the cosmopolitan port city of Antwerp. The only people to show him understanding are an orphan and two disillusioned women.
